Class GameData

java.lang.Object
com.jeopardy.model.GameData
public class GameData extends Object
Represents the complete Jeopardy dataset, consisting of multiple Category objects, each containing their own set of questions.

This class provides utility methods for adding questions/categories, searching by name, and retrieving global statistics such as total categories and total questions.
